Japanese sentences in the Informal Present Negative.
by Mr.Paper » Sat 08.29.2009 2:06 pm Hello! Haven't been on in a while due to school. Well tell me how good my grammar is, thanks. And sentence forming.miruku ga sukkunai namiruku wa yokunai shinjirukyou wa koukou e ikanaitamanegi wa taberu koto ga sukkunai nasoshite, tamago wa taberu koto ga sukkunai nakono bideo geimu ga sukkunai nafuransu ga hanasanai
